{"tid":1831144,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"離鄉別井 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-01-20T07:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T07:36:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd07f3ffd863454a2c5270ea0e255504bc8d5a4d","tid":1831144,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200120/20846681/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200120%2F20846681%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=5690ddc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200120%2F20846681%2F&h=08bf3232\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200120/20846681/</a><br />\n<br />\n離鄉別井 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200120/large/1579416169_3734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579416169_3734.jpg&h=95e741a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那天要坐捷運到龍山寺站附近「青草巷」。受人所托，魚腥草茶包及健康養生青草茶都買一些回港。<br />\n<br />\n在台北車站某角落，見一名年輕人，黑衣黑褲背囊客，他坐在地上抱膝垂首瞌睡，孤單一人，看來很累。我上前問：「你是香港人嗎？」問了兩聲他才抬起頭來，是個清秀的男生──我心血來潮以為是流亡異鄉的手足，總統大選時或亢奮助選，現在人人都「回家」去，他無家可歸？<br />\n<br />\n年輕人抬頭望我一眼，是聽不懂廣東話抑或不是香港人？疲倦的搖頭不答，又再瞌睡去&hellip;&hellip;一路在想，若他是台灣學生，或有累的原因；若他來自香港又是驚弓之鳥，對陌生人一問也只好不答。我離去後眼淚忽然便淌下來。<br />\n<br />\n幾百名流亡台灣的年輕人，十多歲廿多歲學生，或在港有安定工作，一夜之間被迫成為離鄉別井的「難民」，生活和前景一片迷茫。據知有心人已伸出援手，幫助他們繼續讀書（中有優秀大學生和Band 1中學生）、開店、自力更生。支援黃國桐律師的「保護傘」計劃，（可與桐叔及其助理周小姐聯絡）。據知也有不同的組織作人道支援──不知可否把資源和力量聚集一起，把流散的年輕人統籌協助，各界人材除了求學、開店、打工，還發展台港黃色經濟圈，向前看，好好磨練人生。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}